https://dev.mutt.org/trac/wiki/MuttGuide/Folders

inbox  $spoolfile
mbox or received, $mbox, $move 如果想保存或移动邮件离开inbox取代删除他们
sent  $record, $copy 发送的
postponed $postponed  start new email but ehn pause to continue later

inbox默认是系统环境变量$MAIL,除非你设置inbox在你的$HOME,一般指向/var/spool/mail/USER
shortcut  "!" 指 "inbox"   "~"指$HOME  "+"or"="指"folder"也就是mutt的folder
">"之"mbox"     "<"指"sent" $record

set folder=/var/spool/mail/john   设置folder为$MAIL, 里面有INBOX Sent ...等mailboxes
set spoolfile="+INBOX" 收件箱$MAIL/INBOX
set record="+Sent Messages" 发送的邮件保存到$MAIL/Sent\ Messages
set mbox="~/Mail/Seen"  按d删除的邮件或已阅读的邮件，移动到~/Mail/Seen,需要set move=yes, 如果set move=no,这个选项无用, Seen目录下需要有cur tmp new这3个目录，会移动删除的邮件到cur目录, 把阅读的也移动或删除并不好，因为offlineimap会同步到服务器，所以最好还是设置set move=no
set postponed="+Drafts" 延期的邮件保持到$MAIL/Drafts

remote folders可以设置为set folder="imaps://user@example.com"
--------------------------------------------------------------------
set folder=/var/spool/mail/john
### deleted mails by press d key in mutt and which have been read, move them to ~/Mail/QQ-Deleted
### this directory must have three directory tmp cur and new, it will store
### in cur directory. and set move=yes, it it's no then this option won't work
###set mbox="~/Mail/QQ-Deleted"

### if you set delete flag on mail in mutt, then wait offlineimap sync it to ser
ver, and sync delete
### move the deleted mails to where mbox point, if it's not INBOX, and move=yes,
### it will be deleted from INBOX and it's not good when it sync to server
### so just leave it in INBOX
set mbox="+INBOX"

### inbox will be /var/spool/mail/john/INBOX
set spoolfile="+INBOX"

### sent box will be $MAIL/Sent\ Messages
set record="+Sent Messages"

### Drafts
set postponed="+Drafts"
set move=no
-----------------------------------------------------------
c 切换邮箱，比如从INBOX切换到sent, tab或者首字母索引会自动补全
以qq邮箱为例，offlineimap同步下来的有"INBOX" "Junk" "Sent Messages" "Drafts"
"Deleted Messages"

mailboxes "INBOX" "Sent Messages" "Drafts" "Deleted Messages" "Junk"

处理html需要~/.mailcap  text/html; lynx --dump %s; nametemplate=%s.html; copiousoutput

~/.muttrc  auto_view text/html


prevent asking like "~/Mail does not exist create it ?"
set folder=""

prevent asking like "move read message to ~/mbox? no/yes"
set move=no

dont wait for sendmail to finish
set sendmail_wait=-1

